    "description": "<p class=\"attachment\"><a href='https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/analytics-accelerator-service-chart.png'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"576\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/analytics-accelerator-service-chart-576x311.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"There are 3 types of services. Facilitated Training starts with an intro before going into Data Structure &amp; Modeling; Calculations; Data Viz, Design, Access; PowerBI Service &amp; Worfklow; and Data Security &amp; Gov. It then goes to Review. Office Hours &amp; Project Consultation starts with a Scoping Session. There are a series of office hours, a less-frequent series of Project Reviews, with an optional Special IT Engagement. Enduring Collateral has Self-Service Training Materials and Advanced training &amp; materials for Department Champions. This work spans 1-3 months depending on how scoped.\" srcset=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/analytics-accelerator-service-chart-576x311.png 576w, https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/analytics-accelerator-service-chart.png 751w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" /></a></p>\n",
    "caption": "",
    "alt_text": "There are 3 types of services. Facilitated Training starts with an intro before going into Data Structure & Modeling; Calculations; Data Viz, Design, Access; PowerBI Service & Worfklow; and Data Security & Gov. It then goes to Review. Office Hours & Project Consultation starts with a Scoping Session. There are a series of office hours, a less-frequent series of Project Reviews, with an optional Special IT Engagement. Enduring Collateral has Self-Service Training Materials and Advanced training & materials for Department Champions. This work spans 1-3 months depending on how scoped.",
